results.name: Number of relatively prime 3-part integer partitions of n with no 1's.
comment: The Heinz numbers of these partitions are the intersection of A005408 (no 1's), A014612 (length 3), and A289509 (relatively prime).
example: The a(7) = 1 through a(17) = 16 triples (A = 10, B = 11, C = 12, D = 13):
xref: A001399(n-6) does not require relative primality.
A005408 /\ A014612 /\ A289509 gives the Heinz numbers of these partitions.
A284825 counts the case that is also pairwise non-coprime.
A302698 counts these partitions of any length.
A337563 is the pairwise coprime instead of relatively prime version.
A000837 counts relatively prime partitions, with strict case A078374.
A008284 counts partitions by sum and length.
